channel.title: Photoshop Mysteriously Gone?
channel.description:
Today I logged on to my computer and felt like doing some more stuff in photoshop CS2, only to find it mysteriously gone... I'm reinstalling it right now and it says I have 8 days to active it, so my trial didn't run out, but does anyone know why this could of happened?
Oh, and if someone has a CS2 crack they could send me via PM that would be nice.
